          <title>Alyssa Thomas heading to Mercury from Sun in trade, AP source says</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The Phoenix Mercury were finalizing a deal to acquire Alyssa Thomas from the Connecticut Sun, a person familiar with the trade told The Associated Press on Tuesday night. The Sun also will send Ty Harris to Phoenix, while Connecticut will receive Natasha Cloud, Rebecca Allen and the No.]]></description>
